OL,6,     FGermany v Curacao (Kick-off
OL,7,     F6.00pm). Mark Pougatch presents
OL,8,     Fcoverage of the Group E match at
OL,9,     FHouston Stadium in the USA. The
OL,10,     FCaribbean outfit face one of
OL,11,     Ffootball's most decorated nations
OL,12,     Fin their first-ever World Cup
OL,13,     Ffinals match as they go up against
OL,14,     Fthe four-time champions, who have
OL,15,     Falso reached the final on four
OL,16,     Fother occasions. Since their most
OL,17,     Frecent World Cup victory at the
OL,18,     F2014 tournament in Brazil, Die
OL,19,     FMannschaft have failed to progress
OL,20,     Ffrom the group stage and have only
OL,21,     Fwon two matches at the last two
OL,22,     Ftournaments combined. Julian
