OL,5,G0230 FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,     FSweden v Tunisia (Kick-off
OL,7,     F3.00am). Semra Hunter presents
OL,8,     Fcoverage of the Group F match at
OL,9,     FMonterrey Stadium in Mexico.
OL,10,     FSweden have a fairly disappointing
OL,11,     Frecord of qualifying for the World
OL,12,     FCup in recent times, only
OL,13,     Fappearing three times since they
OL,14,     Ffinished third at USA '94, and
OL,15,     Fthey had to rely on the UEFA
OL,16,     Fplay-offs to secure their spot
OL,17,     Fthis time around. For Tunisia this
OL,18,     Fis their third consecutive
OL,19,     Fappearance at a World Cup finals
OL,20,     Fand their seventh overall, and
OL,21,     Fthey'll hope to take advantage of
OL,22,     Fthe new expanded format and
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
